WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:01:50.068 --> 00:01:51.748
It's been near six years

3
00:01:51.778 --> 00:01:54.406
since I last saw
my lord husband. maester.

4
00:01:55.032 --> 00:01:58.243
I must know... will he live?

5
00:01:59.453 --> 00:02:01.997
He led his sailors
into an ambush.

6
00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:04.458
A ship made to look
as if it were abandoned.

7
00:02:05.876 --> 00:02:09.421
In the fighting. his neck was slashed
by a corsair's dagger.

8
00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:12.883
He fell overboard into the sea.

9
00:02:12.966 --> 00:02:14.843
The wound was severe.

10
00:02:14.926 --> 00:02:16.678
Much blood was lost.

11
00:02:16.762 --> 00:02:19.723
But the greater concern
is the fever that followed.

12
00:02:19.806 --> 00:02:22.976
The ship's maester said
he burns from within.

13
00:02:36.114 --> 00:02:37.908
The ravens came in from?

14
00:02:37.991 --> 00:02:39.618
Evenfall. Princess.

15
00:02:41.536 --> 00:02:43.163
So they arrive in three days.

16
00:02:46.041 --> 00:02:48.543
Let all be made ready to receive him.
maester kelvyn.

17
00:02:55.175 --> 00:02:57.386
- The sea snake is strong.
- Hmm.

18
00:02:57.469 --> 00:02:58.637
No doubt.

19
00:02:59.179 --> 00:03:03.225
And yet. I have seen blood fever
overcome men half his age.

20
00:03:03.308 --> 00:03:06.436
I will not suffer the talk
of crows in my house. vaemond.

21
00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.230
I love my brother...

22
00:03:09.106 --> 00:03:11.108
But we must be honest with ourselves.

23
00:03:11.858 --> 00:03:14.027
We may greet his ship to find him gone.

24
00:03:14.111 --> 00:03:16.571
And who will take the driftwood throne?

25
00:03:16.655 --> 00:03:18.448
My grandmother seems
quite comfortable here.

26
00:03:18.532 --> 00:03:21.451
She presides only in the absence
ofherhusband.

27
00:03:22.744 --> 00:03:25.163
On his death. the seat passes.

28
00:03:25.247 --> 00:03:26.456
To lucerys velaryon.

29
00:03:26.540 --> 00:03:28.208
As is my lord husband's desire.

30
00:03:28.291 --> 00:03:31.670
I am the sea snake's own blood.

31
00:03:31.753 --> 00:03:34.256
the closest kin he has left.

32
00:03:34.339 --> 00:03:35.799
Be careful. good-brother.

33
00:03:36.675 --> 00:03:38.427
One could take your words for treason.

34
00:03:47.269 --> 00:03:49.938
I speak the truth. rhaenys.

35
00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.774
And you know it.

36
00:03:54.025 --> 00:03:55.736
The matter has been decided.

37
00:03:55.819 --> 00:03:57.571
By a man whose ambition

38
00:03:57.654 --> 00:04:01.408
has brought down on us
calamity after calamity.

39
00:04:01.491 --> 00:04:04.494
My brother cares only
for the history books.

40
00:04:06.872 --> 00:04:09.082
But what of the velaryon line?

41
00:04:09.166 --> 00:04:11.710
Is it to be snuffed out.

42
00:04:11.793 --> 00:04:14.546
supplanted by the pups of house strong?

43
00:04:15.005 --> 00:04:18.550
Driftmark is mine by all rights.

44
00:04:18.633 --> 00:04:20.594
And while I should like your support.

45
00:04:20.677 --> 00:04:23.680
I do not need it.

46
00:04:25.891 --> 00:04:27.225
The winds have shifted.

47
00:04:28.727 --> 00:04:32.689
The crown has good reason
to take my side.

48
00:04:33.106 --> 00:04:35.859
My cousin the king
would have your tongue for this.

49
00:04:35.942 --> 00:04:40.947
But it's not a king who sits
the iron throne these days. good-sister.

50
00:04:41.865 --> 00:04:43.575
It's a queen.

51
00:07:01.796 --> 00:07:05.216
The conqueror and
his sisters sailed with a great army.

52
00:07:11.723 --> 00:07:14.351
And landed
at the Blackwater rush.

53
00:07:21.691 --> 00:07:23.151
At the end?

54
00:07:23.234 --> 00:07:24.569
- The mouth.
- Mouth!

55
00:07:24.653 --> 00:07:26.863
Oh. come on. Jace. you knew that.

56
00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:36.641
Come on. Jace.

57
00:07:36.665 --> 00:07:40.168
- Perhaps that's enough for this morning.
- No. no. I want to keep going.

58
00:07:41.711 --> 00:07:42.796
Maester.

59
00:07:46.174 --> 00:07:49.594
Aegon... ordered
that the trees should be...

60
00:07:50.512 --> 00:07:52.430
- Killed.
- Felled.

61
00:07:52.514 --> 00:07:53.932
It is a related word.

62
00:07:54.391 --> 00:07:56.643
I don't expect you to learn
high valyrian in a day. Jace.

63
00:07:56.726 --> 00:08:00.021
A king should honor
the traditions of his forbears.

64
00:08:00.105 --> 00:08:02.816
Well... unless you're planning

65
00:08:02.899 --> 00:08:05.902
to depose your own mother.
you have plenty of time to study.

66
00:08:14.285 --> 00:08:15.495
Leave us.

67
00:08:17.497 --> 00:08:19.290
Joffrey... come.

68
00:08:40.103 --> 00:08:42.731
He means to call into question
Luke's legitimacy.

69
00:08:44.274 --> 00:08:46.109
And by extension. Jace.

70
00:08:46.192 --> 00:08:48.319
and by extension.
my own claim to the throne.

71
00:08:48.403 --> 00:08:51.614
Vaemond cares only about driftmark
and the velaryon line.

72
00:08:52.532 --> 00:08:54.159
Not about our politics.

73
00:08:54.993 --> 00:08:56.846
Has he made common cause
with Otto hightower yet?

74
00:08:56.870 --> 00:08:58.997
Mmm. This is what I fear.

75
00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:01.082
Rhaenys has flown to court.

76
00:09:01.166 --> 00:09:02.846
Surely. she cannot
be planning to back him.

77
00:09:02.876 --> 00:09:04.919
No. Whatever disagreements
we may have had.

78
00:09:05.003 --> 00:09:06.337
she's not cruel...

79
00:09:06.963 --> 00:09:09.799
- Or stupid enough to do that.
- Disagreements?

80
00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:12.969
She believes we had her son killed
so that we might marry.

81
00:09:13.053 --> 00:09:16.848
Yes... and yet.
she's taken baela to ward.

82
00:09:16.931 --> 00:09:19.601
Yes. It is laena's memory she honors.
She has no love for us.

83
00:09:21.478 --> 00:09:23.730
Has the vipers' venom spread so far?

84
00:09:23.813 --> 00:09:26.232
Those vipers rule in my father's name.

85
00:09:27.025 --> 00:09:28.651
And my father...

86
00:09:35.450 --> 00:09:36.951
What choice do I have?

87
00:09:43.583 --> 00:09:44.834
To king's landing. then.

88
00:10:26.334 --> 00:10:29.504
All hail rhaenyra
of house Targaryen.

89
00:10:29.587 --> 00:10:32.048
Princess of dragonstone
and heir to the iron throne

90
00:10:32.132 --> 00:10:35.760
and her royal consort.
prince daemon Targaryen.

91
00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:11.671
Welcome back. Princess.

92
00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:13.631
Lord caswell.

93
00:11:23.558 --> 00:11:26.352
I would say it's nice to be home.
but I scarcely recognize it.

94
00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:28.270
Hmm.

95
00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:37.155
We have continued
to enjoy improved customs duties

96
00:11:37.238 --> 00:11:40.158
since the settling of the stepstones.

97
00:11:40.241 --> 00:11:42.952
And the extent to which we exploit those

98
00:11:43.036 --> 00:11:47.207
is contingent on
the harbor master's receipts.

99
00:11:47.582 --> 00:11:49.209
Of which. um.

100
00:11:49.292 --> 00:11:52.629
Uh. the septons have requested

101
00:11:52.712 --> 00:11:54.923
half that again for a bronze bust

102
00:11:55.006 --> 00:11:56.466
they wish to commission

103
00:11:56.549 --> 00:11:58.551
for the festival of the mother...

104
00:11:58.635 --> 00:11:59.969
Which I would not recommend.

105
00:12:00.053 --> 00:12:02.972
Thank you for that exhaustive
accounting. lord beesbury.

106
00:12:03.056 --> 00:12:04.265
I remind you...

107
00:12:11.940 --> 00:12:13.816
Your guests have arrived. your grace.

108
00:12:13.900 --> 00:12:16.611
I trust they've been welcomed
as befits their station.

109
00:12:16.694 --> 00:12:18.279
As you instructed. lord hand.

110
00:12:20.448 --> 00:12:24.410
It was my understanding lord corlys
wished for his grandson lucerys

111
00:12:24.494 --> 00:12:26.246
to succeed him as lord of the tides.

112
00:12:26.329 --> 00:12:29.540
The boy has been raised most of his life
away from driftmark.

113
00:12:30.375 --> 00:12:33.753
He can fly a dragon. yes.
but can he command a fleet?

114
00:12:33.836 --> 00:12:36.172
Ability does not alter his claim.

115
00:12:36.256 --> 00:12:39.175
The sea snake has never
formally named him as heir.

116
00:12:39.259 --> 00:12:40.677
if it comes to that.

117
00:12:40.760 --> 00:12:43.137
The crown must choose
what is best for the realm.

118
00:12:43.221 --> 00:12:45.974
He is laenor's son.
What grounds could there be...

119
00:12:46.057 --> 00:12:48.101
What indeed. lord beesbury.

120
00:12:48.184 --> 00:12:49.852
What indeed.

121
00:12:50.979 --> 00:12:52.498
We shall hear
Princess rhaenyra's petition.

122
00:12:52.522 --> 00:12:54.642
along with those of the other claimants
on the morrow.

123
00:12:54.691 --> 00:12:56.943
I do beg your pardon. my lords.

124
00:12:57.610 --> 00:12:59.070
I must greet our guests.

125
00:13:04.492 --> 00:13:07.370
Shall we Levy a tax
on the sale of new wool?

126
00:13:07.453 --> 00:13:09.163
Your grace...

127
00:13:09.247 --> 00:13:11.291
A matter has arisen
that requires your attention.

128
00:13:11.374 --> 00:13:13.501
Whatever it is. serarryk.
it'll need to wait.

129
00:13:13.584 --> 00:13:17.297
- I'm erryk. your grace.
- Of course. My apologies. ser.

130
00:13:17.380 --> 00:13:19.007
It's about the prince.

131
00:13:19.090 --> 00:13:21.509
There's been a delicate situation
in his apartments.

132
00:13:53.666 --> 00:13:54.667
Father?

133
00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:23.112
- Who goes there?
- Father.

134
00:14:24.572 --> 00:14:26.783
It's me. my king.

135
00:14:27.950 --> 00:14:29.160
Rhaenyra.

136
00:14:37.460 --> 00:14:38.878
I'm here with daemon.

137
00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.631
Daemon?

138
00:14:42.215 --> 00:14:43.424
Daemon?

139
00:14:45.927 --> 00:14:47.220
Daemon.

140
00:14:50.556 --> 00:14:51.974
Help me up.

141
00:15:09.283 --> 00:15:10.910
It has been so long.

142
00:15:16.958 --> 00:15:20.128
The sea snake has taken a grave wound
in battle in the stepstones.

143
00:15:20.545 --> 00:15:24.090
When?

144
00:15:24.173 --> 00:15:26.634
We won that war years ago.

145
00:15:29.095 --> 00:15:30.763
The triarchy is resurgent.

146
00:15:32.181 --> 00:15:33.558
The fighting is anew.

147
00:15:35.017 --> 00:15:38.855
There's... there is a petition to decide
upon the succession of driftmark

148
00:15:38.938 --> 00:15:40.940
and the heir to the driftwood throne.

149
00:15:43.818 --> 00:15:44.819
Petitions?

150
00:15:47.655 --> 00:15:51.742
Alicent and Otto...
They see to all that business now.

151
00:15:51.826 --> 00:15:53.911
No. brother. listen to me.

152
00:15:54.787 --> 00:15:57.206
You are to affirm
your position for lucerys...

153
00:15:58.249 --> 00:16:00.251
To be corlys velaryon's successor.

154
00:16:02.837 --> 00:16:04.797
Has something happened
to lord corlys?

155
00:16:07.592 --> 00:16:09.343
Father...

156
00:16:09.427 --> 00:16:11.721
There's someone we wish
to introduce you to.

157
00:16:30.031 --> 00:16:31.491
Daemon.

158
00:16:33.493 --> 00:16:34.494
Brother.

159
00:16:37.455 --> 00:16:38.873
Who is that?

160
00:16:40.708 --> 00:16:41.709
Father...

161
00:16:43.586 --> 00:16:45.505
This is aegon.

162
00:16:46.964 --> 00:16:47.965
Aegon.

163
00:16:49.258 --> 00:16:51.844
And this... is viserys.

164
00:16:55.932 --> 00:16:57.391
Viserys.

165
00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:04.857
Now that is a name fit for a king.

166
00:17:13.366 --> 00:17:16.118
Oh. oh...

167
00:17:16.202 --> 00:17:17.328
I'm sorry.

168
00:17:18.412 --> 00:17:20.998
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

169
00:17:22.291 --> 00:17:23.334
I'm so...

170
00:17:26.629 --> 00:17:29.382
I'm sorry. I'm sor...

171
00:17:29.465 --> 00:17:30.633
Please.

172
00:17:32.093 --> 00:17:35.680
- My tea. My tea.
- What tea? This?

173
00:17:35.763 --> 00:17:37.598
Yes. Yes.

174
00:17:39.559 --> 00:17:40.768
Yes.

175
00:17:47.358 --> 00:17:48.609
Ah!

176
00:18:09.505 --> 00:18:11.966
I brought her here immediately.

177
00:18:12.049 --> 00:18:13.509
She's seen no one else. your grace.

178
00:18:19.056 --> 00:18:20.057
Come here. sweetling.

179
00:18:30.901 --> 00:18:31.901
Tell me your name.

180
00:18:35.239 --> 00:18:37.199
It's dyana. your grace.

181
00:18:39.660 --> 00:18:40.786
If it please you.

182
00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:45.416
Dyana. What a pretty name.

183
00:18:48.753 --> 00:18:51.213
I understand you've found
yourself in some trouble.

184
00:18:54.467 --> 00:18:56.302
I was fetching the prince his wine.

185
00:18:56.385 --> 00:19:00.097
and I put it on his table.
and when I turned...

186
00:19:01.265 --> 00:19:02.391
I didn't see him.

187
00:19:03.934 --> 00:19:06.145
I asked him to stop. your grace.

188
00:19:06.228 --> 00:19:08.522
I did. truly...

189
00:19:09.106 --> 00:19:10.441
You must believe me.

190
00:19:24.997 --> 00:19:26.415
Thank you for telling me. dyana.

191
00:19:32.171 --> 00:19:33.422
I know it wasn't your fault.

192
00:19:36.550 --> 00:19:37.551
I believe you.

193
00:19:38.469 --> 00:19:39.595
You do?

194
00:19:41.305 --> 00:19:42.306
I do.

195
00:19:45.476 --> 00:19:46.852
But what I worry about...

196
00:19:48.688 --> 00:19:49.980
Is what others might believe.

197
00:19:52.733 --> 00:19:54.493
You were alone with the prince.
were you not?

198
00:19:55.277 --> 00:19:57.571
Yes. I...

199
00:19:57.655 --> 00:19:59.895
And no one else saw what happened
between the two of you.

200
00:20:01.117 --> 00:20:03.411
If anyone else were to hear about this...

201
00:20:03.494 --> 00:20:04.662
I haven't told anyone.

202
00:20:04.745 --> 00:20:07.248
You told ser erryk
and talya and now me.

203
00:20:08.541 --> 00:20:09.976
And though I believe
you are not to blame.

204
00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:11.419
others might not be so trusting.

205
00:20:13.337 --> 00:20:16.017
They might think you were trying
to besmirch the prince. or worse...

206
00:20:17.133 --> 00:20:18.193
That you're the sort of girl

207
00:20:18.217 --> 00:20:20.136
that might have enticed him
in the first place.

208
00:20:22.096 --> 00:20:23.856
And you know what happens
to girls like that.

209
00:20:26.183 --> 00:20:30.646
I wouldn't dream of breathing
another word to anyone. your grace.

210
00:20:32.064 --> 00:20:34.066
I swear it on my life.

211
00:20:41.532 --> 00:20:42.533
I know you won't.

212
00:20:56.046 --> 00:20:57.047
For your troubles.

213
00:21:05.014 --> 00:21:06.432
The tea. your grace.

214
00:21:21.447 --> 00:21:22.656
It's best to be certain.

215
00:21:50.434 --> 00:21:51.977
Get up.

216
00:21:52.061 --> 00:21:53.103
Aegon!

217
00:21:56.482 --> 00:21:57.483
Get up!

218
00:22:01.403 --> 00:22:02.404
Mother?

219
00:22:03.823 --> 00:22:07.368
- What is it?
- "What is it? What is it?

220
00:22:07.451 --> 00:22:09.221
What is it?"
That's all you can say for yourself?

221
00:22:09.245 --> 00:22:10.830
Has something happened?

222
00:22:11.747 --> 00:22:12.748
Dyana.

223
00:22:12.832 --> 00:22:13.832
Hmm?

224
00:22:14.375 --> 00:22:15.455
The serving girl.

225
00:22:18.087 --> 00:22:19.713
For the gods' sake.

226
00:22:19.797 --> 00:22:22.299
The girl. aegon. The one
you sent fleeing from your company.

227
00:22:22.383 --> 00:22:25.177
Oh. it was just harmless fun.

228
00:22:25.261 --> 00:22:28.472
She didn't need to go
and get upset about it.

229
00:22:28.556 --> 00:22:31.517
Think of the shame on your wife. on me.

230
00:22:32.893 --> 00:22:35.187
How can you keep carrying on like this.

231
00:22:35.271 --> 00:22:37.147
especially on a day like today?

232
00:22:37.231 --> 00:22:38.649
Why? What is it today?

233
00:22:53.706 --> 00:22:54.874
You are no son of mine.

234
00:23:01.463 --> 00:23:03.465
I did not ask for this.

235
00:23:03.549 --> 00:23:05.885
I've done everything you've asked me to.

236
00:23:05.968 --> 00:23:06.968
and I try so...

237
00:23:08.137 --> 00:23:11.348
I try so hard. but it will never
be enough for you or father.

238
00:23:13.851 --> 00:23:16.729
Have you seen dyana?
She's supposed to dress the children.

239
00:23:25.154 --> 00:23:26.655
He looks like a different person.

240
00:23:28.282 --> 00:23:31.785
I believe we should also
consult maester gerardys.

241
00:23:31.869 --> 00:23:34.269
Perhaps if he could see the king.
he'd suggest a different...

242
00:23:34.788 --> 00:23:36.832
Princess rhaenyra.

243
00:23:36.916 --> 00:23:37.917
And prince daemon.

244
00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:39.000
Hmm.

245
00:23:40.961 --> 00:23:44.298
It has been so long since we were
granted the joy of your presence.

246
00:23:47.343 --> 00:23:48.677
Indeed. your grace.

247
00:23:48.761 --> 00:23:51.430
Though not long enough
to merit a greeting upon our arrival.

248
00:23:52.473 --> 00:23:55.059
I'm sure the queen
had pressing business. my love.

249
00:23:56.060 --> 00:23:58.437
What can either of us
know of ruling a kingdom?

250
00:23:58.520 --> 00:24:01.231
I do not rule. as you well know.

251
00:24:01.315 --> 00:24:03.943
My father and I are mere
stewards of the king's will and wisdom.

252
00:24:04.026 --> 00:24:06.362
And how exactly
is that wisdom expressed?

253
00:24:08.656 --> 00:24:10.407
In blinks and wheezes?

254
00:24:10.491 --> 00:24:12.493
I'd be surprised if he could remember
his own name.

255
00:24:12.576 --> 00:24:14.453
- Or if you could.
- King viserys's condition

256
00:24:14.536 --> 00:24:16.456
has worsened since you saw him last.

257
00:24:17.915 --> 00:24:19.750
It subjects him to considerable pain.

258
00:24:19.833 --> 00:24:22.252
- On the advice of the maesters...
- Oh. the maesters.

259
00:24:22.795 --> 00:24:24.964
Of course. It is they who keep him...

260
00:24:26.006 --> 00:24:29.593
Addled on milk of the poppy
while the hightowers warm his throne.

261
00:24:29.677 --> 00:24:31.762
Rhaenyra. if you would
see him without it.

262
00:24:31.845 --> 00:24:33.931
- almost blind with suffering.
- Oh.

263
00:24:34.014 --> 00:24:37.434
Alicent. I have no doubt
it was an act of the purest mercy.

264
00:24:37.518 --> 00:24:39.979
but tell me. for the king's suffering.

265
00:24:40.062 --> 00:24:42.940
did the maesters also prescribe
the removal of Targaryen heraldry

266
00:24:43.023 --> 00:24:45.651
and the installation in its stead
of various statues and stars?

267
00:24:46.860 --> 00:24:48.278
The emblems of the seven serve only

268
00:24:48.362 --> 00:24:50.340
to guide us on an uncertain path.

269
00:24:50.364 --> 00:24:53.075
- To remind us of a higher authority.
- And on the morrow.

270
00:24:53.158 --> 00:24:54.785
which authority will sit in judgment

271
00:24:54.868 --> 00:24:56.662
of my son's claim
on his own inheritance?

272
00:24:57.830 --> 00:25:00.230
- That would be mine... and the hand's.
- Ah.

273
00:25:00.290 --> 00:25:02.626
But be assured.
the father is just and commands me

274
00:25:02.710 --> 00:25:05.170
to forget the accusations
you have hurled in this room today.

275
00:25:12.011 --> 00:25:14.638
- Smaller than I remember.
- It looks exactly the same.

276
00:25:15.597 --> 00:25:16.598
Oh. Luke. come on.

277
00:25:32.614 --> 00:25:35.159
See? I told you
this would still be here.

278
00:25:35.242 --> 00:25:37.911
And you thought you could swing
criston's morningstar.

279
00:25:38.579 --> 00:25:40.581
And you almost took your own head off.

280
00:25:46.045 --> 00:25:48.589
- What's your problem?
- Everyone's staring at us.

281
00:25:48.672 --> 00:25:49.715
Yeah!

282
00:25:52.134 --> 00:25:54.720
No one would question me
being heir to driftmark...

283
00:25:57.806 --> 00:26:00.017
If I looked more
like ser laenor velaryon

284
00:26:00.100 --> 00:26:01.518
than ser hannin strong.

285
00:26:03.228 --> 00:26:04.772
It doesn't matter what they think.

286
00:26:50.275 --> 00:26:51.777
Well done. my prince.

287
00:26:51.860 --> 00:26:53.340
You'll be winning tourneys
in no time.

288
00:26:53.403 --> 00:26:55.114
I don't give a shit about tourneys.

289
00:26:56.365 --> 00:26:57.366
Nephews...

290
00:26:58.867 --> 00:27:00.077
Have you come to train?

291
00:27:01.036 --> 00:27:02.454
Open the gate!

292
00:27:36.822 --> 00:27:38.490
Hold your nerve. my queen.

293
00:27:38.574 --> 00:27:40.993
What we do.
we do for the good of the realm.

294
00:27:41.076 --> 00:27:44.955
I must confess a certain uneasiness
now this is at hand.

295
00:27:45.914 --> 00:27:49.668
- He may yet live.
- But we must be prepared if he does not.

296
00:27:58.552 --> 00:28:01.346
The realm has enjoyed a long peace.

297
00:28:01.430 --> 00:28:04.308
a credit to the work of both
jaehaerys and viserys.

298
00:28:04.391 --> 00:28:08.103
but the threat of war looms
and may arrive on our shores.

299
00:28:08.187 --> 00:28:11.273
When it does.
will you want a child at the command

300
00:28:11.356 --> 00:28:13.192
of the greatest fleet in Westeros?

301
00:28:15.152 --> 00:28:16.904
Oh. we must. of course...

302
00:28:18.363 --> 00:28:20.490
Act in the interest of our subjects.

303
00:28:22.534 --> 00:28:25.662
The next lord of the tides
will be deeply in your debt. your grace.

304
00:28:27.039 --> 00:28:28.332
As will driftmark...

305
00:28:28.957 --> 00:28:29.958
In all its strength.

306
00:28:47.768 --> 00:28:48.852
Grandmother?

307
00:28:53.106 --> 00:28:54.191
Rhaena.

308
00:29:02.115 --> 00:29:03.825
Baela said you might be here.

309
00:29:06.119 --> 00:29:07.829
She's done well as your ward.

310
00:29:07.913 --> 00:29:09.122
You've. um...

311
00:29:10.499 --> 00:29:11.917
Raised her admirably.

312
00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:13.794
You honor me. Princess.

313
00:29:15.420 --> 00:29:17.798
Might I speak
to the Princess alone. rhaena?

314
00:29:21.385 --> 00:29:22.386
Princess.

315
00:29:32.396 --> 00:29:37.943
I wondered for many an hour
what your purpose was in coming here.

316
00:29:38.026 --> 00:29:41.071
Whether you'd speak for or against
the suit brought by ser vaemond.

317
00:29:41.154 --> 00:29:42.781
But then. I realized...

318
00:29:43.865 --> 00:29:45.867
You intend to advocate for yourself.

319
00:29:49.288 --> 00:29:51.957
This is no fair proceeding.

320
00:29:52.040 --> 00:29:55.961
It is a trap set by the queen
and the hand. I'd wager.

321
00:29:56.044 --> 00:29:57.879
to proclaim my son illegitimate.

322
00:29:57.963 --> 00:30:00.090
Yet you did worse than that with laenor.

323
00:30:03.093 --> 00:30:04.177
Did you not?

324
00:30:10.642 --> 00:30:12.185
I loved your son.

325
00:30:14.646 --> 00:30:16.940
You may not believe it
to be true. but I did.

326
00:30:21.361 --> 00:30:23.530
I did not order his death.

327
00:30:25.991 --> 00:30:28.327
Nor was I complicit in it.
I swear this to you.

328
00:30:36.335 --> 00:30:37.794
I'll make you an offer.

329
00:30:41.340 --> 00:30:42.549
Back Luke's claim.

330
00:30:42.632 --> 00:30:44.801
and let us betroth
laena's children to mine.

331
00:30:47.304 --> 00:30:50.891
Baela will be
queen of the seven kingdoms

332
00:30:51.933 --> 00:30:53.643
and her sons
will be heirs to the throne.

333
00:30:54.728 --> 00:30:57.731
Rhaena will rule in driftmark. and...

334
00:30:57.814 --> 00:31:00.317
The seat will pass to her and lucerys's
children in time.

335
00:31:00.901 --> 00:31:02.194
A generous offer.

336
00:31:04.696 --> 00:31:06.907
- Or a desperate one.
- What does it matter?

337
00:31:12.245 --> 00:31:13.525
You are right in this. at least.

338
00:31:18.502 --> 00:31:19.836
It does not matter.

339
00:31:30.305 --> 00:31:31.785
You can bargain with me all you like.

340
00:31:33.558 --> 00:31:36.144
Bring my granddaughter
with you to soften my resolve.

341
00:31:37.813 --> 00:31:40.982
But tomorrow.
the hightowers land their first blow.

342
00:31:42.859 --> 00:31:45.237
They force you to your knees...

343
00:31:45.987 --> 00:31:47.406
And I must stand alone.

344
00:32:31.408 --> 00:32:32.409
Alicent?

345
00:32:34.161 --> 00:32:35.662
Alicent...

346
00:32:35.745 --> 00:32:37.038
No. it's rhaenyra. father.

347
00:32:42.085 --> 00:32:43.170
Rhaenyra.

348
00:32:49.676 --> 00:32:52.679
"The song of ice and fire."
Do you believe it to be true?

349
00:32:55.765 --> 00:32:57.350
Aegon's dream.

350
00:33:01.605 --> 00:33:03.231
You told me

351
00:33:03.315 --> 00:33:06.651
it was our duty to hold
the realm united against a common foe.

352
00:33:11.364 --> 00:33:13.325
By naming me heir.
you divided the realm.

353
00:33:24.503 --> 00:33:26.046
I thought I wanted it.

354
00:33:36.598 --> 00:33:38.058
But the burden is a heavy one.

355
00:33:41.311 --> 00:33:44.231
It's too heavy.

356
00:33:53.573 --> 00:33:54.908
My only child.

357
00:34:00.038 --> 00:34:02.541
If you wish me to bear it.
then defend me.

358
00:34:04.501 --> 00:34:05.669
And my children.

359
00:34:10.131 --> 00:34:11.258
It's...

360
00:35:07.564 --> 00:35:09.274
I want to have supper. Otto.

361
00:35:12.402 --> 00:35:15.572
- It is the morning. your grace.
- Tonight.

362
00:35:18.908 --> 00:35:20.327
The whole of my family

363
00:35:21.703 --> 00:35:23.413
are gathered at the red keep.

364
00:35:26.124 --> 00:35:29.294
I want us to dine together.

365
00:36:00.533 --> 00:36:01.910
Bring milk of the poppy.

366
00:36:17.050 --> 00:36:18.051
No.

367
00:36:21.221 --> 00:36:22.472
Just arrange the supper.

368
00:36:28.436 --> 00:36:30.397
Though it is the great hope
of this court

369
00:36:30.480 --> 00:36:33.942
that lord corlys velaryon
survive his wounds.

370
00:36:34.818 --> 00:36:37.195
we gather here with the grim task

371
00:36:37.278 --> 00:36:39.739
of dealing with
the succession of driftmark.

372
00:36:41.199 --> 00:36:44.369
As hand. I speak with
the king's voice on this

373
00:36:44.452 --> 00:36:45.578
and all other matters.

374
00:36:48.415 --> 00:36:50.208
The crown will now hear the petitions.

375
00:36:51.501 --> 00:36:53.169
Ser vaemond of house velaryon.

376
00:37:01.553 --> 00:37:02.762
My queen.

377
00:37:04.180 --> 00:37:05.390
My lord hand.

378
00:37:06.725 --> 00:37:09.811
The history of our noble houses
extends beyond the seven kingdoms

379
00:37:09.894 --> 00:37:11.896
to the days of old valyria.

380
00:37:11.980 --> 00:37:14.858
For as long as house Targaryen
has ruled the skies.

381
00:37:14.941 --> 00:37:17.569
house velaryon has ruled the seas.

382
00:37:17.652 --> 00:37:19.404
When the doom fell on valyria.

383
00:37:19.487 --> 00:37:22.157
our houses became
the last of their kind.

384
00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:25.577
Our forebearers came to this new land.
knowing that were they to fail.

385
00:37:25.660 --> 00:37:28.413
it would mean the end
to their bloodlines and their name.

386
00:37:30.373 --> 00:37:34.127
I have spent my entire life on driftmark
defending my brother's seat.

387
00:37:34.210 --> 00:37:38.131
I am lord corlys's closest kin.
his own blood.

388
00:37:38.214 --> 00:37:42.427
The true. unimpeachable blood
of house velaryon runs through my veins.

389
00:37:42.510 --> 00:37:46.264
As it does in my sons.
the offspring of laenor velaryon.

390
00:37:46.347 --> 00:37:49.100
If you cared so much
about your house's blood. servaemond.

391
00:37:49.184 --> 00:37:51.454
you would not be so bold as
to supplant its rightful heir.

392
00:37:51.478 --> 00:37:54.939
No. you only speak for yourself
and for your own ambition.

393
00:37:55.023 --> 00:37:57.460
You will have chance to make
your own petition. Princess rhaenyra.

394
00:37:57.484 --> 00:38:00.153
Do ser vaemond the courtesy
of allowing his to be heard.

395
00:38:05.992 --> 00:38:08.036
What do you know
of velaryon blood. Princess?

396
00:38:09.996 --> 00:38:13.041
I could cut my veins and show it to you

397
00:38:13.124 --> 00:38:16.544
and you still wouldn't recognize it.

398
00:38:16.628 --> 00:38:20.465
This is about the future
and survival of my house. not yours.

399
00:38:25.512 --> 00:38:27.222
My queen. my lord hand.

400
00:38:28.973 --> 00:38:31.684
This is a matter of blood. not ambition.

401
00:38:33.144 --> 00:38:38.024
I place the continuation of the survival
of my house and my line above all.

402
00:38:38.107 --> 00:38:41.319
I humbly put myself before you
as my brother's successor...

403
00:38:42.445 --> 00:38:45.532
The lord of driftmark
and lord of the tides.

404
00:38:47.075 --> 00:38:48.284
Thank you. ser vaemond.

405
00:38:55.625 --> 00:39:01.130
Princess rhaenyra. you may now speak
for your son. lucerys velaryon.

406
00:39:06.594 --> 00:39:09.305
If I am to grace this farce
with some answer.

407
00:39:09.389 --> 00:39:13.017
I will start by reminding the court
that nearly 20 years ago. in this very...

408
00:39:18.147 --> 00:39:21.109
King viserys of house Targaryen.

409
00:39:21.192 --> 00:39:23.194
the first of his name.

410
00:39:23.278 --> 00:39:27.699
king of the andals and the rhoynar
and the first men.

411
00:39:28.741 --> 00:39:32.620
lord of the seven kingdoms
and protector of the realm.

412
00:40:53.159 --> 00:40:55.078
I will sit the throne today.

413
00:40:56.955 --> 00:40:57.997
Your grace.

414
00:41:05.588 --> 00:41:08.007
I will be fine. I will be fine.

415
00:41:22.230 --> 00:41:23.648
I said I'm fine.

416
00:41:27.485 --> 00:41:28.486
Come on.

417
00:41:35.952 --> 00:41:37.370
Steady.

418
00:42:18.828 --> 00:42:23.708
I must... admit... my confusion.

419
00:42:25.918 --> 00:42:28.171
I do not understand

420
00:42:28.254 --> 00:42:32.633
why petitions are being heard
over a settled succession.

421
00:42:32.717 --> 00:42:33.885
The only one present...

422
00:42:35.011 --> 00:42:39.640
Who might offer keener insight
into lord corlys's wishes

423
00:42:39.724 --> 00:42:41.517
is the Princess rhaenys.

424
00:42:45.271 --> 00:42:46.272
Indeed. your grace.

425
00:43:00.828 --> 00:43:03.956
It was ever my husband's
will that driftmark

426
00:43:04.040 --> 00:43:06.709
pass through ser laenor

427
00:43:06.793 --> 00:43:08.377
to his trueborn son...

428
00:43:09.420 --> 00:43:11.547
Lucerys velaryon.

429
00:43:11.631 --> 00:43:13.341
His mind never changed.

430
00:43:14.425 --> 00:43:16.636
Nor did my support of him.

431
00:43:17.637 --> 00:43:19.305
As a matter of fact.
the Princess rhaenyra

432
00:43:19.388 --> 00:43:20.890
has just informed me of her desire

433
00:43:20.973 --> 00:43:22.642
to marry her sons Jace and Luke

434
00:43:22.725 --> 00:43:25.561
to lord corlys's granddaughters.
baela and rhaena.

435
00:43:26.979 --> 00:43:30.608
A proposal to which I heartily agree.

436
00:43:32.068 --> 00:43:35.488
Well... The matter is settled.

437
00:43:36.948 --> 00:43:38.324
Again.

438
00:43:39.450 --> 00:43:44.747
I hereby reaffirm
prince lucerys of house velaryon

439
00:43:44.831 --> 00:43:46.999
as heir to driftmark.

440
00:43:47.083 --> 00:43:51.087
the driftwood throne.
and the next lord of the tides.

441
00:43:58.427 --> 00:44:00.054
You break law...

442
00:44:01.222 --> 00:44:02.974
And centuries of tradition

443
00:44:03.933 --> 00:44:06.144
to install your daughter as heir.

444
00:44:07.186 --> 00:44:08.938
Yet you dare tell me...

445
00:44:10.022 --> 00:44:12.567
Who deserves
to inherit the name velaryon.

446
00:44:17.572 --> 00:44:19.699
I will not allow it.

447
00:44:20.658 --> 00:44:21.742
"Aiiow it"?

448
00:44:23.202 --> 00:44:25.413
Do not forget yourself. vaemond.

449
00:44:29.458 --> 00:44:34.046
That is no true velaryon.

450
00:44:34.130 --> 00:44:37.341
and certainly no nephew of mine.

451
00:44:37.425 --> 00:44:39.510
Go to your chambers.
You have said enough.

452
00:44:40.928 --> 00:44:44.348
Lucerys is my true-born grandson.

453
00:44:45.391 --> 00:44:46.934
And you...

454
00:44:47.018 --> 00:44:50.521
Are no more
than the second son of driftmark.

455
00:44:51.606 --> 00:44:56.235
You... may run your house
as you see fit...

456
00:44:57.320 --> 00:45:00.114
But you will not decide
the future of mine.

457
00:45:02.200 --> 00:45:04.243
My house survived the doom

458
00:45:04.327 --> 00:45:07.496
and a thousand tribulations besides.

459
00:45:07.580 --> 00:45:09.332
And gods be damned...

460
00:45:10.583 --> 00:45:16.297
I will not see it ended
on the account of this...

461
00:45:18.007 --> 00:45:19.008
Say it.

462
00:45:29.977 --> 00:45:31.103
Her children...

463
00:45:32.230 --> 00:45:34.106
Are bastards!

464
00:45:37.818 --> 00:45:39.111
And she...

465
00:45:41.822 --> 00:45:42.907
A whore.

466
00:45:52.708 --> 00:45:54.126
Will have your tongue for that.

467
00:46:01.676 --> 00:46:03.052
He can keep his tongue.

468
00:46:04.303 --> 00:46:05.805
- Disarm him!
- No need.

469
00:46:14.438 --> 00:46:16.399
- Call the maesters!
- Father?

470
00:46:16.482 --> 00:46:18.943
Please. my love.
You must take something for the pain.

471
00:46:20.403 --> 00:46:21.904
I will not cloud my mind.

472
00:46:23.072 --> 00:46:25.324
I must put things right.

473
00:47:10.494 --> 00:47:14.540
The body will be ready for its return
to driftmark on the morrow. my lady.

474
00:47:17.793 --> 00:47:20.796
You may wish to leave the silent sisters
to their work.

475
00:47:21.881 --> 00:47:24.550
It is ill luck to look
upon the face of death.

476
00:47:28.888 --> 00:47:32.767
The stranger has visited me more times
than I can count. grand maester.

477
00:47:37.813 --> 00:47:38.939
I assure you...

478
00:47:40.358 --> 00:47:43.778
He cares little whether my eyes
are open or closed.

479
00:49:09.738 --> 00:49:13.325
How good it is
to see you all tonight...

480
00:49:14.452 --> 00:49:15.744
Together.

481
00:49:21.542 --> 00:49:23.586
- Prayer before we begin?
- Yes.

482
00:49:25.588 --> 00:49:27.882
May the mother smile down
on this gathering with love.

483
00:49:28.841 --> 00:49:32.553
May the Smith mend the bonds
that have been broken for far too long.

484
00:49:32.636 --> 00:49:35.848
And to vaemond velaryon.
may the gods give him rest.

485
00:49:43.898 --> 00:49:46.734
This is an occasion for celebration.
it seems.

486
00:49:47.776 --> 00:49:50.362
My grandsons. Jace and Luke.

487
00:49:50.446 --> 00:49:53.616
will marry their cousins.
baela and rhaena.

488
00:49:53.699 --> 00:49:56.452
further strengthening the bond
between our houses.

489
00:49:57.119 --> 00:49:59.580
A toast to the young princes...

490
00:50:00.539 --> 00:50:02.917
- And their betrothed.
- Hear. hear!

491
00:50:04.001 --> 00:50:06.587
Well done. Jace.
You'll finally get to lie with a woman.

492
00:50:07.588 --> 00:50:10.633
Let us toast as well prince lucerys...

493
00:50:12.134 --> 00:50:14.803
The future lord of the tides.

494
00:50:14.887 --> 00:50:16.388
Hear. hear.

495
00:50:16.472 --> 00:50:17.472
You'll be great.

496
00:50:21.560 --> 00:50:24.980
You do know
how the act is done. I assume?

497
00:50:25.940 --> 00:50:27.066
At least in principle?

498
00:50:27.149 --> 00:50:28.589
Where to put your cock and all that.

499
00:50:28.651 --> 00:50:30.027
Let it be. cousin.

500
00:50:30.110 --> 00:50:31.779
You can play the Jester if you wish.

501
00:50:31.862 --> 00:50:33.906
but hold your tongue
before my betrothed.

502
00:50:33.989 --> 00:50:34.989
Hmm.

503
00:50:55.427 --> 00:50:58.556
It both gladdens my heart

504
00:50:59.932 --> 00:51:02.560
and fills me with sorrow

505
00:51:04.228 --> 00:51:07.273
to see these faces around the table.

506
00:51:08.691 --> 00:51:11.902
The faces most dear
to me in all the world...

507
00:51:13.862 --> 00:51:15.990
Yet grown so distant from each other...

508
00:51:17.074 --> 00:51:18.367
In the years past.

509
00:51:43.017 --> 00:51:44.351
My own face...

510
00:51:45.728 --> 00:51:47.938
Is no longer a handsome one...

511
00:51:50.649 --> 00:51:52.276
If indeed it ever was.

512
00:51:55.863 --> 00:51:56.989
But tonight...

513
00:51:57.990 --> 00:52:01.076
I wish you to see me as I am.

514
00:52:02.620 --> 00:52:04.246
Not just a king...

515
00:52:05.914 --> 00:52:07.124
But your father.

516
00:52:08.876 --> 00:52:09.960
Your brother.

517
00:52:10.836 --> 00:52:11.962
Your husband...

518
00:52:14.923 --> 00:52:16.258
And your grandsire.

519
00:52:17.593 --> 00:52:19.053
Who may not. it seems...

520
00:52:20.596 --> 00:52:22.389
Walk for much longer among you.

521
00:52:28.479 --> 00:52:30.397
Let us no longer hold

522
00:52:30.481 --> 00:52:32.399
ill feelings in our hearts.

523
00:52:34.151 --> 00:52:35.861
The crown cannot stand strong

524
00:52:35.944 --> 00:52:38.322
if the house of the dragon
remains divided.

525
00:52:39.573 --> 00:52:41.492
But set aside your grievances.

526
00:52:45.746 --> 00:52:47.956
If not for the sake of the crown...

527
00:52:48.874 --> 00:52:50.793
Then for the sake of this old man

528
00:52:52.211 --> 00:52:53.420
who loves you all

529
00:52:54.880 --> 00:52:55.923
so clearly.

530
00:53:23.242 --> 00:53:26.245
I wish to raise my cup
to her grace. the queen.

531
00:53:30.499 --> 00:53:31.667
I love my father.

532
00:53:32.876 --> 00:53:35.295
But I must admit
that no one has stood...

533
00:53:36.380 --> 00:53:38.590
More onally by his side
than his good wife.

534
00:53:42.094 --> 00:53:43.887
She has tended to him with...

535
00:53:45.222 --> 00:53:47.182
Unfailing devotion.

536
00:53:47.266 --> 00:53:49.893
love. and honor.

537
00:53:51.061 --> 00:53:53.897
And for that. she has my gratitude...

538
00:53:55.691 --> 00:53:56.775
And my apology.

539
00:54:06.660 --> 00:54:09.496
Your graciousness
moves me deeply. Princess.

540
00:54:12.583 --> 00:54:13.917
We are both mothers

541
00:54:17.045 --> 00:54:18.255
and we love our children.

542
00:54:22.342 --> 00:54:25.012
We have more in common
than we sometimes allow.

543
00:54:28.182 --> 00:54:31.518
I raise my cup to you and to your house.

544
00:54:37.107 --> 00:54:38.400
You will make a fine queen.

545
00:55:17.231 --> 00:55:19.525
I regret the disappointment
you are soon to suffer.

546
00:55:20.692 --> 00:55:24.112
But if you ever wish to know
what it is to be well satisfied.

547
00:55:24.196 --> 00:55:26.365
all you have to do is ask.

548
00:55:26.824 --> 00:55:27.825
Jace.

549
00:55:56.687 --> 00:56:00.774
To prince aegon and prince aemond.

550
00:56:00.858 --> 00:56:04.152
We have not seen each other in years.

551
00:56:04.236 --> 00:56:07.072
but I have fond memories
of our shared youth.

552
00:56:09.408 --> 00:56:13.036
And as men. I hope we may
yet befriends and allies.

553
00:56:14.496 --> 00:56:17.124
To you and your family's
good health. dear uncles.

554
00:56:25.007 --> 00:56:26.008
To you as well.

555
00:56:33.932 --> 00:56:36.310
Beware the beast beneath the boards.

556
00:56:36.393 --> 00:56:37.811
Well done. my boys.

557
00:56:37.895 --> 00:56:40.355
I would like to toast
to baela and rhaena.

558
00:56:41.398 --> 00:56:42.733
They'll be married soon.

559
00:56:44.526 --> 00:56:47.112
It isn't so bad.
Mostly he just ignores you...

560
00:56:48.864 --> 00:56:50.782
Except sometimes when he's drunk.

561
00:56:59.207 --> 00:57:01.877
- Good.
- Let us have some music.

562
00:57:07.841 --> 00:57:09.092
Excuse me.

563
00:58:40.934 --> 00:58:42.574
Guards.

564
00:58:50.610 --> 00:58:51.987
Please. sit down.

565
00:59:31.693 --> 00:59:32.778
Final tribute.

566
00:59:36.031 --> 00:59:37.532
To the health of my nephews.

567
00:59:38.909 --> 00:59:39.909
jace_.

568
00:59:41.536 --> 00:59:42.536
Luke_.

569
00:59:43.830 --> 00:59:44.956
And Joffrey.

570
00:59:46.291 --> 00:59:49.252
Each of them handsome. wise...

571
00:59:56.968 --> 00:59:58.470
- Strong.
- Aemond.

572
00:59:58.553 --> 00:59:59.554
Come...

573
01:00:01.431 --> 01:00:04.643
Let us drain our cups to these three...

574
01:00:05.727 --> 01:00:07.979
- Strong boys.
- I dare you to say that again.

575
01:00:08.063 --> 01:00:10.482
Why? 'Twas only a compliment.

576
01:00:11.149 --> 01:00:13.068
Do you not think yourself strong?

577
01:00:13.193 --> 01:00:15.445
- Jace!
- That is enough!

578
01:00:22.202 --> 01:00:24.371
Why would you say such a thing
before these people?

579
01:00:24.454 --> 01:00:27.666
I was merely expressing how proud I am
of my family. mother.

580
01:00:27.749 --> 01:00:31.378
Mmm. Though it seems my nephews
aren't quite as proud of theirs.

581
01:00:31.461 --> 01:00:32.629
Wait. wait!

582
01:00:36.967 --> 01:00:39.469
Go to your quarters.
All of you go. now.

583
01:00:51.189 --> 01:00:52.189
Hmm.

584
01:00:59.489 --> 01:01:00.490
Rhaenyra.

585
01:01:04.452 --> 01:01:07.205
It's best. I think.
if we go back to dragonstone.

586
01:01:07.289 --> 01:01:08.790
You've only just arrived.

587
01:01:15.255 --> 01:01:16.506
Let me see the children home.

588
01:01:18.133 --> 01:01:19.426
I'll. um...

589
01:01:20.552 --> 01:01:21.845
Return on dragonback.

590
01:01:26.933 --> 01:01:29.144
The king and I would both like that.

591
01:02:10.518 --> 01:02:13.855
It's been quite a night
at the castle. it seems.

592
01:02:15.106 --> 01:02:16.149
Yes. my lady.

593
01:02:51.559 --> 01:02:52.811
Come on. come on.

594
01:02:56.898 --> 01:02:57.899
- That's it.
- Igu! Ps}

595
01:03:10.870 --> 01:03:12.080
Well done.

596
01:03:18.920 --> 01:03:21.381
I'm sorry.

597
01:03:21.464 --> 01:03:22.716
I'm sorry.

598
01:03:25.844 --> 01:03:27.387
But you wanted to know...

599
01:03:28.722 --> 01:03:30.932
If I believe it to be true.

600
01:03:32.767 --> 01:03:34.394
Believe what to be true. my king?

601
01:03:35.478 --> 01:03:36.855
Don't you remember?

602
01:03:39.149 --> 01:03:40.358
Aegon...

603
01:03:43.028 --> 01:03:44.029
Our son?

604
01:03:46.406 --> 01:03:47.490
His dream.

605
01:03:48.491 --> 01:03:51.828
The song of ice... and fi...

606
01:03:53.246 --> 01:03:54.247
It is true.

607
01:03:55.665 --> 01:03:57.250
What he saw in the north.

608
01:04:00.211 --> 01:04:01.921
The prince that was promised.

609
01:04:03.340 --> 01:04:04.758
I don't understand. viserys.

610
01:04:06.259 --> 01:04:07.802
The prince.

611
01:04:07.886 --> 01:04:09.054
Prince aegon?

612
01:04:10.722 --> 01:04:12.515
To unite the realm

613
01:04:12.599 --> 01:04:15.393
against the cold... and the dark.

614
01:04:19.272 --> 01:04:20.398
It is you.

615
01:04:23.777 --> 01:04:25.070
You are the one.

616
01:04:27.238 --> 01:04:28.698
You must do this.

617
01:04:30.784 --> 01:04:32.452
You must do this.

618
01:05:17.705 --> 01:05:18.832
I understand. my king.

619
01:05:40.061 --> 01:05:41.354
No more.

620
01:05:42.063 --> 01:05:43.064
No more.

621
01:06:12.427 --> 01:06:13.511
My love.

